			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. Add Shadowheart's mom to the camp&#xD;&#xA;2, Talk to her" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="92" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Default camp dialog for Shadowheart's mom. She has recovered somewhat from her ordeal in the Shar grotto, but will never truly heal - she's grown old in captivity, and she's prone to confusion at times. Still, she remains glad and supportive.&#xD;&#xA;She has unique branches for Shadowheart and non-Shadowheart players, as well as branches that occur before and after CAMP_Shadowheart_DaughterTears, in which SH and her parents have their first proper heart to heart." />
